movie_name: Becoming Hitchcock: The Legacy of Blackmail

movie_name: The Man Who Definitely Didn't Steal Hollywood
short_description: Giancarlo Parretti's $1.3B purchase of MGM in 1990 leads to an FBI probe over irregularities. His ownership crumbles amid lawsuits and charges. He flees before sentencing but is arrested as the investigation uncovers global corrup...
